The paper deals with enhancing a system model, which suggests that it falls under the category of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the operational and denotational semantics of timed port automata, which are used to model state-boxes, indicating that it could also be classified under Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). The paper also deals with composition of components, which is a topic in Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
